column1: Technical notes for India: These estimates may not be regarded as the national statistics officially produced by India due to differences arising from the data and methods used by WHO. The information from the Civil Registration System in India for 2020 was made publicly available by the Registrar General of India on 3 May 2022 in a report at: https://crsorgi.gov.in/annual-report.html. The newly published information in the report is being carefully examined and will be taken into consideration in revisions of the estimates.
